Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As night falls upon the\Nforest around these parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it becomes so perilous it hardly\Nseems like it belongs to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you please, feel free to take\Nmy carriage to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, there is. You're welcome\Nto visit Dr. Hogback's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Man Called a Genius!\NHogback Makes His Appearance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... The fog kept me from\Ngetting a good look at the horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't they seem a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you must be imagining things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...? I hope that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're a lifesaver!\NThanks for saving our hides!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing! Please, have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest is filled with unusual animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it dangerous to simply walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was surprised! I thought\NCerberus was an imaginary animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That terrifying beast must\Nbe a mutant or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid we were gonna be stuck\Nin that tree when you found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mansion is the best place\Nto wait for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stands out and it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll get to meet Dr. Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he all that famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single doctor\Nwho doesn't know his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a famous surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his miraculous operations, he's saved\Nas many people as there are stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has obtained status, honor,\Nand everything you could get as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's earned the respect of\Ndoctors around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then he suddenly vanished one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some say he went missing,\Nwhile others say he was abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It threw the medical world\Ninto an uproar for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end, no one could find any leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's on the verge of becoming a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant that Dr. Hogback, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! The doctor is \Nstill conducting research
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that goes beyond the\Nboundary of human knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I \Nasked for his autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you want,\NI'm sure that would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest... even has lions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?! Don't freak me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just now, I saw a l-lion outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't buy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take a look for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prey... Fresh prey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prey! Fresh prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird stuff's out there!\NSuper weird stuff's out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right here! Stop the \Ncarriage, Hildon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so worked up?\NAre you having hallucinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a hallucination!\NI'm sure they were out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest is way too messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose. This forest is a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The combination of thick fog and fear\Ncan induce hallucinations in some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That was a hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now? A hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was too vivid for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp, gulp, gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hildon-san! Sorry, but could\Nyou take us back to the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's dangerous, we'll manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I won't get to meet Dr. Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I get how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is when we've gotta listen to\Nour special Something's Fishy Sensors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you willing to die to meet that doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you skip meeting him\Nso we can leave this island alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't want to die! Or get scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? I shall \Ngo inform the coachmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chopper! I know\Nyou're passing up a huge chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped! I'm still green,\Nsince I can't act on my own like Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"10 Minutes Later..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shhh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is he going to keep us waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. We're just\Ngoing back the way we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No one's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the horses are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They abandoned us in a graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They what?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! They abandoned us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure they aren't going potty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hildon! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:10:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the places, why'd they\Nhave to choose a graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Jeez, I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to remind me where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:11:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carriage is gonna fall over!\NThey're insanely strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now I'm gonna turn into a zombie!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't bite me! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, save me! They're about to bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Let go of me! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies are weak against...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Flame Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fire!\N--That's rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That worked better than I could have hoped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous, you pyro punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I actually caught on fire,\Nyou stupid jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ticked off the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, the mansion's the\Nclosest place to run to for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay! They can't catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we run like mad for the mansion\Nonce we're outta the graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies can only walk at a\Nsnail's pace and groan at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"At a snail's pace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"At a snail's pace"? "At a snail's pace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"At a snail's pace"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No--er, huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec... Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are carrying the ship away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping you, Gah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Gah," punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we used the paddle,\Nwe could fight the waves, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on going to the island anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go with the flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! You've totally forgotten\Nabout Nami-san, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:15:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spider web on the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to\Nram right into the spider web.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we need the paddle! Release the paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! It didn't harm the ship,\Nbut now we're stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is this spider \Nweb so freakishly big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They... aren't chasing us anymore, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this island?! It's oozing\Nwith stuff that shouldn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, if I turn into a zombie,\Nfinish me off in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you come up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the Illustrated Zombie Guide\NI read in Sunny's library!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a scaredy-cat, you read\Nway too many of those books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're here. Right now,\NI just want a glass of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to meet him after all. I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone in his right mind\Nwould live on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bet on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Is this Dr. Hogback's mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're traveling pira--sailors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got lost and could use some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this mansion?\NA tunnel runs through the center of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a courtyard on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe no one's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would stink! We'll have to\Nface zombies if we turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! A light in the back turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a light, it's \Na spotlight for this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:08.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:10.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman's throwing plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six, seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it seem like she's goin' after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am! I cannot invite \Nyou into the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two may step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Hold your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more scary stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can make this\None exception, Cindry-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if she startled you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, this woman was\Nengaged to her wealthy master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To test his love, she broke\Nall of his prized plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tossed her out, and her \Ntragic past has made her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,develop an aversion to plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my servant, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I really don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've failed to introduce myself.\NI am the world-renowned Dr. Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ten!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Cindry-chan,\NI said you could stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me look bad\Nwhen you don't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish plates would disappear\Nfrom the face of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand! I understand completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was in the middle of a conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, is he the guy \Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dr. Hogback in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may talk inside.\NToday, I will make an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, right! Come inside my mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why I wasn't welcome,\Nbut should we take them up on the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Beats the zombies outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to welcome you to my mansion.\NBut my, you sure are grungy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole bunch of things, but for starters--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything in detail later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:20:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies attacked us in the graveyard,\Nso we ran here for cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a whole bunch of stuff\Nthat made us doubt our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you live here,\Nyou've gotta know something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So they attacked you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you made it here\Nin one piece. That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To answer your question:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they are,\Nwhich is why I live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're conducting research on the zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are terrified when they hear "zombie."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I rephrase it\Nto "resurrecting the dead"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't that been all mankind's eternal dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a special someone or two\Nthey'd like to see return from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But toying with human mortality is\Nunorthodox medicine that disrespects God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I slipped away\Nfrom the public eye--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could continue my\Nresearch on this island in secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So that's the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure tons of people\Naround the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be thrilled if your \Nresearch is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be rooting for you, Dr. Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather open-minded!\NThank you, Dr. Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shucks, Doctor! I'm not happy because\Nyou thanked me or anything, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Dr. Chopper..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Dr. Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show me your lab later?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, steer clear of my laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cindry-chan! Put the flan on plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish plates would disappear\Nfrom the face of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, I wash the heck out of the\Ntablecloth for times just like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so feel free to eat away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still use your spoons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn you a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a filthy lot, so go hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops. He doesn't mean anything to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but did a weird skeleton\Ndrop by before we arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's tall with an afro\Nand he's oddly cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the fact that he's a talking,\Nwalking skeleton makes him odd enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be him? Nah, it couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, why do I have to\Nstand watch while you bathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! We're leaving as soon as night falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, how could you say that?!\NThere are zombies outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to yourself! Do you seriously\Nthink the mansion is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami's in a Major Pinch! The Zombie\NMansion and the Invisible Man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
